products.productdescription:
The splash oyster light filtering skylight blind is a very light, natural cream colour perfect for a skylight window. This neutral tone will work well in most spaces. The blind comes with sleek, modern aluminium framework which is also available in a white colour. Their skylight blinds also have the option to include a control rod for those more difficult to reach windows. As with all their made to measure products this blind will come with a 5 year guarantee for extra peace of mind.
